citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 12:20pm on 09-
JAN-23. An inspector called the number on file with no answer and a voicemail was left. The licensee called back right
away and confirmed that no responsible adult was able to be present for an inspection that day.
Additional Inspectors:
HARVEY KENT, VETERINARY MEDICAL OFFICEREnd Section
